    serviceDescription:
      "eSakor Portal delivers land transactions services to the citizens of Bhutan.",
    serviceLink: "https://esakor.nlcs.gov.bt/",
    serviceDocument:
      '<p><font face="Times New Roman" size="4"><b style=""><font color="#0a0000" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">SERVICE&nbsp; NAME:</font><span style="color: rgb(254, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 150, 255);"> Land Transaction Services</span></b></font></p><p><b style="background-color: transparent; color: var(--bs-modal-color); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); letter-spacing: 0.0178571em;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><font color="#090101">BRIEF DESCRIPTION:</font></font></b><br></p><p><font color="#050505" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">eSakor Portal is a portal for changing the way the National Land Commission of Bhutan delivers land transactions services to the citizens of Bhutan. The portal was launched on 8th Jan, 2019 by the NLCS, and gives citizens access to land transaction services without having to visit a NLCS or Thromde office.</span></font></p><p><font color="#050505" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">Bhutanese citizens can create an account using their ID card number. Once registered, one can use the portal to do land transaction.</span></font></p><p><font color="#050505" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">Document</span></font></p><p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#0a0000"><span style="background-color: transparent; text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); letter-spacing: 0.0178571em; font-weight: bolder;">PROCEDURE:&nbsp;</span></font></p><ul><li><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#090101">Sign in the system</font></li><li><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#090101">Fill in the online forms</font></li><li><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#090101">Add transaction details</font></li><li><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#090101">Upload scanned copy of supporting documents and</font></li><li><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#090101">Submit the transaction application</font></li></ul><p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#050000"><b><i>Note:</i></b></font></p><p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#0a0000">Any status changes at any stage will be notified to the applicant through email,\nSMS in registered mobile number and in the notifications center in applicants portal\naccount.</font></p><p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#120202"><span style="font-weight: bolder; background-color: transparent; text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); letter-spacing: 0.0178571em;">CONTACT DETAILS:</span></font></p><p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify;"><font style="" color="#050505">If you have any issues / inquiry on how to use system please feel free to contact during office hours or drop an email in the email address given. We will reply your email within one or two working days. Please read the</font></span></font><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><a href="https://esakor.nlcs.gov.bt/portal/public/app/guide" target="_blank"> "Guides on eSakor Portal"</a></font><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify;"><font style="" color="#050505"> provided in the portal before directly contacting us.</font></span></font></p><p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#050000"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">+975-02-325170 (ICT Division, NLCS)</span><span style="letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify;"><br></span></font></p><p style="text-align: left;"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><font color="#050000">&nbsp;support@nlcs.gov.bt</font></span><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><font color="#0a0a0a" style=""><br></font></span></font></p><p></p><p></p>',
