    serviceDescription:
      "The registration of competent person, import authorization, technical authorization and renewal of competent person as well as technical authorization.",
    serviceLink: "https://www.citizenservices.gov.bt/NDI/?agency=dra",
    serviceDocument:
      '<span id="docs-internal-guid-ea618ed0-7fff-3009-9c9b-4e8bdc0babe9" style=""><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; cursor: auto; line-height: 2.316; user-select: text !important;"><font size="4" style=""><span style="font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); user-select: text !important;"><font color="#000000" style="" face="Times New Roman">SERVICE NAME:</font></span><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(0, 150, 255); user-select: text !important;"><font face="Times New Roman" style=""> Bhutan Food and Drug Authority</font></span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; cursor: auto; line-height: 2.316; user-select: text !important;"><font size="3" style="" face="Times New Roman"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve; user-select: text !important;">BRIEF DESCRIPTION:</span></font></p><ol style=""><li style=""><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">The Medical Product Division (MPD) of the Bhutan Food and Drug Authority (BFDA) plays a vital role in safeguarding public health through the regulation of medical products. The division is dedicated to ensuring that all medical products entering Bhutan meet the required standards of safety, quality, and efficacy. To achieve this, the MPD performs a range of regulatory functions aimed at protecting public health and maintaining high standards in the countrys medical product sector.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">One of the division\'s key responsibilities is market authorization, ensuring that medical products are thoroughly assessed and approved before they are made available for use in Bhutan. The MPD also conducts ongoing vigilance through post-market surveillance, closely monitoring the safety and effectiveness of medical products once they are in use. Regulatory inspections are regularly carried out at manufacturing facilities, distribution centers, and storage sites to ensure compliance with safety and quality standards.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">In addition, the MPD is responsible for technical authorizations related to both the manufacture and sale of medicinal products. This includes granting approval for the manufacturing of medical products in Bhutan and regulating their sale and distribution within the country. The division also oversees the registration of competent persons, ensuring that only qualified professionals are authorized to handle, manufacture, or distribute medical products.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">Another important function is the lot release of vaccines, where the division ensures that all vaccines meet safety and quality standards before they are released to the public. The MPD also manages import and export authorization, regulating the flow of medical products across Bhutans borders while ensuring they meet both national and international standards. Market control and surveillance are carried out to monitor the availability and use of medical products in the market, ensuring that all products continue to comply with regulations. Lastly, the division oversees clinical trial oversight, ensuring that clinical trials are conducted in compliance with ethical standards and regulatory requirements.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">These services and functions align with the nine core functions required of a National Regulatory Authority (NRA) as set out by the World Health Organization (WHO), ensuring that Bhutans regulatory framework for medical products is comprehensive, robust, and internationally recognized.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><br></span></font></p><p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3" color="#ffffff"><span style="letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(12, 152, 212);"><b style="">The Following key services of the Bhutan Food and Drug Authority&nbsp; can be availed in this portal:</b></span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">1. Registration of Competent people</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">2. Renewal of Competent People.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">3. Application for Import authorization for medicinal products.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">4. Application for Technical authorization for sale and distribution of medicinal Products</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">5. Application for Technical authorization Manufacture of medicinal products</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">6. Renewal of Technical Authorization.</span></font></p><p><font color="#1b1b1b" face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">7. Change of Technical Authorization details.</span></font></p></li></ol><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"></p></span>',
